---
import Base from '../../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE, t } from '../../../../data/i18n.js';
const lang = 'pt';
---
<Base lang={lang} title="Visita Guiada a Segóvia — Reserve com María Victoria" description="Visita guiada a Segóvia. Aqueduto, Alcázar, Catedral. Guia diplomada." path="/segovia/visita-guiada/">
  <div class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 overflow-hidden">
    <img src="/img/segovia/acueducto-noche.webp" alt="Aqueduct of Segovia" class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="1600" height="1097" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Visita Guiada</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-sepia mb-8">Segóvia — Património da Humanidade UNESCO</p>
    <section class="mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Duração</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">Flexível</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Preço</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">Sob consulta</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Idiomas</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">PT · ES · EN · IT · FR</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>Um percurso do Aqueduto romano ao Alcázar, passando pela Catedral e a Casa da Moeda Real de Filipe II.</p>
        <p>Para quem quer Segóvia além do leitão. Combina com El Escorial e Ávila.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="cta-green rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Reserve a sua visita</h2>
      <p class="text-sepia mb-4">Contacte diretamente María Victoria</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34659953930?text=Olá%20María%20Victoria%2C%20gostaria%20de%20uma%20visita%20a%20Segóvia" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block btn-whatsapp px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium">💬 WhatsApp</a>
      <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70 mt-4">Resposta habitual em menos de 24 horas</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
